[src:git/git-branch] If this option is omitted, the name of the current branch will be used instead.
[src:git/git-branch] The same restrictions as for *<branch-name>* apply.
[src:git/git-branch] `pager.branch` is only respected when listing branches, i.e., when `--list` is used or implied.
